@eivindreke Hej! Vi kan tyvärr inte se vad som orsakar problemet med ombokningen för din biljett härifrån, men om det inte fungerar via vår hemsida/app så rekommenderar jag att du ringer oss på tel +47 21 896 400 för hjälp med ombokningen.

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@PaulKeeper99 HI, please contact us through our chat or phone with questions regarding a specifik booking or flight in a booking.   https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Regards,
Peter

@TheJmaster6 Hello!
If you have cancelled/rebooked your booking online due to a cancelled flight or schedule change then there is a possibility the website doesn't recognize the cause of this action and apply the ticket rules. Please contact us by chat or phone so we can assist you!

//Emilia

@nameandnums Hi, please make sure that you are not using a VPN connection when browsing our website. If the problem persists please try a different web browser, or if possible a difference device or network to see if that helps.

Best regards,
Anton.

@JohannesSkov Hi, I recommend you to contact our support between 8:00-16:00 CET so we can have a deeper look into what is going on here. You can find our phone numbers and live chat here: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj - Please select your region in the drop down menu.
Kind regards, 
Rebecka

@larsgaardhoj Hej, jag är ledsen att du har problem att boka resor på vår hemsida. Har du fortfarande problem efter att du rensat cache/cookies eller testat en annan webbläsare, vänligen ring oss så vi kan hjälpa dig att boka resan.  +4570102000
Vänliga hälsningar, 
Rebecka

@TollMarcus Hej!
Jag är ledsen att ert bagage är försenat. Det bästa jag kan rekommendera i så fall är att kontakta bagageservicen så att de kan kontrollera statusen för ditt ärende. Du hittar numren för bagageservice här: https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2

Hälsningar Anja!

@wallseany Hi!

We have received your case and your case is currently being handled by our Customer Care department. Please allow some more time for them to respond to you.

Best regards / Sanna

@LuukDobbe Hi! 

Customer Care do have a pretty long queue right now due to the situation with Covid-19 but i would recommend that you contact our chat/phone in this case, so we can send them a reminder to look through your case.

//Best regards, Dennis.

@eivindreke Hello! 
The invoice is usually canceled within a few days. If the invoice is not canceled automatically, I would like to ask you to contact us via our live chat or by phone and we will take a look at the case. You will find our contacts here: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj 

//Anja!

@LeanneFarring15 Hi! 

I'm sorry for the late answer. I hope you received the help you needed. The best we can recommend in that case is to call our customer service by phone so we can help you change it. 

//Best regards, Dennis.

@sheirla3 Hello!
In order for us to guarantee that you can bring the pram on board, you need a ticket that includes hand luggage and that the dimensions must not exceed the dimensions 55 cm x 40 cm x 23 cm (length x width x depth).

Thanks for contacting us, regards Anja!

@Jessica48495394 Hi! The information that is followed by the airports can be found here: https://t.co/YhT9mVc7De

You also find more detailed information here: https://t.co/I5lXILKAf5
Kind regards, Rebecka

@Anna70730085 Hi, we usually launch flights 300-330 days in advance but it may look different depending on destination. Available flights can be found on our website: https://t.co/Ec5v80W12W
Stay updated via our social media, website or press room for any news: https://t.co/RL3DxnfqaC
// Sanna

@Netzih Hello, please contact customer service on live-chat or phone https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj and they can help you take a look at what possibilities there are.

Best regards,
Anton.

@Anna70730085 Hi! 

We sadly don't know when we will be able to offer that route again, but we will announce it on our website as soon as we know more about it! 

//Best regards, Dennis.

@kasapluie_ Hi! 

I'm sorry to see that you have a problem with changing your trip, but if you get that error then it's probably a temporary bug, so i recommend that you call our customer service by phone so we can help you with that.

//Best regards, Dennis.

@robertshaye Hi! 

Okay! You can contact our customer service via the chat/messenger in that case. You can find our live-chat on this site: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

//Best regards, Dennis.

@TheHermanHo Hi, I recommend that you call us, or chat with us in our live chat or via Facebook messenger so that we can look at how we can help you in the best way with your question.

You can find our contact information here: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj
Kind regards / Sanna

@kyle_tink93 Hello!
We do not have any business tickets for flights within Europe. Many travel agencies call our SAS PLUS ticket a premium economy. If you need help checking the willingness of the booking class you have booked, you can contact us here: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Regards, Anja!

@kyle_tink93 Hi! Main differences is in the ticket rules: https://t.co/SUGh1L1hGV
When travelling to USA/Asia you have more room and comfort in a SAS Plus seat compared to a regular and business is more comfortable than SAS Plus.
Kind regards, Rebecka

@damonspencer Hi! I recommend you to either call or chat with us for the best possible assistance. You can find our phone numbers and live chat here: https://t.co/b3QIqPBI2R
We can also be reached on Facebook Messenger where we respond as soon as we can.
Kind regards, Rebecka

@Aps5Needs Hi, I am sorry to hear you were charged for the Attestation form. You can normally find it here: https://t.co/gml5ZaEizi - under USA restrictions at the bottom. 
If you would like to submit a complaint you can do so here: https://t.co/wprQ9Zejqh
Kind regards, Rebecka

@olvrwn Hello!

SAS as an airline does not require a test or documentation for the traveler to travel with us, but a facemask is required. The staff at check-in will check your travel documents and any tests if the country you are traveling to requires this.

Best / Emilia

@pswexler Hi, please contact our support on live chat or by phone for further assistance: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj 
I also recommend you to edit your tweets to remove the case id as it is a personal identifier that shouldn't be placed on the internet.
Kind regards, Rebecka

@schultzois Hi! I'm sorry to hear you feel that way.
you can send a complaint to our customer care department, it is important for us to be able to improve our work. You can contact them here via this link:
https://t.co/OzrIxYNv63 select "General Complaint or compliment. Best regards Jonna.
